highlights.text: “Up” by Cardi B is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #19.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 210 weeks straight.
The Weeknd has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Save Your Tears” is the highest at #2.
“The Hills” by The Weeknd is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 146 spots at #52.
